---
title: Rainbow Tomato Flatbread with Mozzarella, Pesto and Arugula
description: It’s hard to go wrong with vibrant cherry tomatoes and herby pesto. We’re letting these ingredients shine in a simple flatbread recipe that couldn’t be easier to prepare. If you know in advance you’ll be making this recipe, let your dough come to room temperature ahead of time—it’ll be easier to roll out!
